text:
Bertil Fiskesjö (July 9, 1928 – 30 November 2019) was a Swedish politician. He was a member of the Centre Party. Fiskesjö was born in Algutsboda.
He was a member of the Riksdag from 1971 to 1994. He later was the Third Deputy Speaker of the Riksdag from 1986 to 1994.

annotations.surface_form: Third Deputy Speaker of the Riksdag
